\par \pard\plain \s19\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\sl276\slmult1\ql\sb0\sa140\ltrpar{\loch
Odoo 11.0 \u8216\'91deb\u8217\'92 package currently supports }{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.debian.org/releases/stretch/" }{\fldrslt {\rtlch \ltrch\langfe255\alang255\cf9\lang255\ul\ulc0\loch
